https://www.bernardmarr.com/default.asp?contentID=1373#:~:text=One%20of%20the%20ways%20Twitter,relevant%20tweets%20for%20every%20individual.&text=Artificial%20intelligence%20tools%20are%20also,improve%20the%20overall%20user%20experience.

== AGENT

Twitter

== GOAL

To improve tweet recommendations

== DATA

Twitter uses data from its users which includes tweets with pictures, without pictures, how many likes and how many retweets a tweet has

== METHODS

Twitter uses a Ranking Algorithm which passes information such as if the tweet contains a picture etc, into a deep neural system which decides the likelyhood a user will like what is being recommended to them on their feed

== RESULTS

twitters new process of recommending tweets increased its daily active users by 14% in Q1 of 2017

== ISSUES

No issues

== SCORE

5

== COMMENTS

This is not really the most interesting application of Machine Learning as I feel this does not really do anything that improves an aspect of our lives but rather, increases our consumption of social media.
